title: #92Noon College Hockey Feast
description: Dean Evason opens the show as his Wild beat the Ducks yesterday and face the Blues tonight...then it's on to the college hockey feast, featuring SCSU's Brett Larson, Gophers' Bob Motzko, Mankato's Mike Hastings, Bemidji's Tom Serratore and UMD's Scott Sandelin! Final hour is the Birk Bit, then Jonny Athletic on the NBA trade deadline!
